'''Eric R. Murray''' is an [[United States|American]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.
Murray has competed as Eric Murray.
Murray was inducted into the [[American Contract Bridge League]]'s Hall of Fame in 2001.<ref name="ACBL HOF">{{cite web 
 | title = Hall of Fame
 | author = 
 | publisher = ACBL
 | url = http://www.acbl.org/about/hall-of-fame/members/murray-eric
 | date =
 | accessdate = 2016-07-31 }}</ref>

